MyPass è una PMI di innovazione tecnologica proprietaria di un'innovativa tecnologia interoperabile di identificazione, accesso, pagamento e smart billing. MyPass trasforma il controllo accessi in sistemi a tecnologia sicura, semplici e meno costosi, atti ad evitare code, attese e biglietterie. 
Questo innovativo sistema è operativo nelle APP: 
- MyPass Ski;
- MyPass Venezia;
- InPark Udine.

Star Yacht Group is a yacht service agency based in Sardinia with the office in Porto Cervo.

Morena Bonfadini founded the company in 2007. Along the years Morena and her team have been creating a strong relationship with their Clients, based on trust and loyalty. They always guarantee a high quality of support, assuring at the same time a prompt response to their every need. The staff is competent and experienced, capable of dealing with complex situations, in complete synergy with owners, captains, chefs, engineers and all crew members, guaranteeing a 24/7 professional service.

As a primary yacht agency of the Mediterranean sea Star Yacht Group is able to offer:

Logistic Support;
Berth Reservations, Visa Formalities and Customs Procedures;
Food Provisioning;
Techical Assistance and Chandler;
Fuel Bunkering;
Interior Supplies;
as well as other yacht services  and support. Click here for the complete list of Services.

Whether your stay in Sardinia is for business or pleasure, SYG team will support you, providing the world class services you and your crew expect and require from a reliable yacht agency such as it is. Star Yacht Group offers a group of selected, track-proven providers, capable of delivering outstanding quality at competitive prices. Punctuality, reliability, trustworthiness and kindness are its master values, with a smile and the willingness to satisfy all the Clients’ needs.

The company can provide support not only in Sardinia and Corsica, but also in several other ports of the Mediterranean sea, such as Naples, Capri, Ischia, Portofino, Isola D’Elba and further, France and Spain.
